    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="fr">The Commission can accept Amendments 8 and 9 in full, Amendments 10 in principle and Amendment 11 in part. These amendments all improve the text by clarifying its requirements, by removing possible areas of misinterpretation or by including additional background material, sensible and logical additional requirements and by increasing the level of protection</j.0:event_legal_comment>
